isted laparoscopic converted to laparoscopic / Robot-assisteret laparoskopisk konverteret til laparoskopisk</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ProcedureType.html#ProcedureType-robot_converted_open\">robot_converted_open</a></td><td>Robot-assisteret laparoskopisk konverteret til åben</td><td>Robot assisted laparoscopic converted to open / Robot-assisteret laparoskopisk konverteret til åben</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ProcedureType.html#ProcedureType-onstep\">onstep</a></td><td>Onstep</td><td>Onstep</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Andet indgreb</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
